)\">Matt. 7:17-18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110061\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110061)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110061)\">2 Tim. 3:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114764\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114764)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114764)\">D&amp;C 86:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108203\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108203)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108203)\">Matt. 24:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108249\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108249)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108249)\">Matt. 26:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111278\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111278)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111278)\">2 Ne. 28:6-14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111302\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111302)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111302)\">2 Ne. 29:6-14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112090\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112090)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112090)\">Alma 30:14-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115393\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115393)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115393)\">D&amp;C 107:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116232\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116232)\">